Description: Slitherlink (also known as Fences, Takegaki, Loop the Loop, Loopy, Ouroboros, Suriza and Dotty Dilemma) is a logic puzzle developed by publisher Nikoli. It first appeared in Puzzle Communication Nikoli #26 (June 1989).
More info: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Slitherlink
